As far as I know you will have to go throught the index and verify the=20
field field (that is not an error) of each term:

			IndexReader reader 	=3D IndexReader.open("index");
			TermEnum 	te 		=3D reader.terms();=20
		=09
			while ( te.next() ) {
			=09
				Term tt =3D te.term();
			=09
				String fieldOfTerm =3D tt.field();
			=09
				if ( fieldOfTerm.compareTo( "contents" ) ) {

					do_something_silly()...
			=09
				} else if ( fieldOfTerm.compareTo( "path" ) ) {

					do_something_silly2()...
				}
			}


-neil




