Hi, all

I want to count all words in a index. I do this:

=2D ---------------------------
        IndexReader reader =3D IndexReader.open( "MyIndex" );
        TermEnum terminos =3D reader.terms();

	int countWords =3D 0;
        while( terminos.next() ) {
               TermDocs td =3D reader.termDocs( terminos.term() );
                while( td.next() )  countWords +=3D td.freq();
        }
=2D ----------------------------

but this is very slow in a large document number. =20
Could somebody say to me how to do this of another faster form?=20

Thank you very much in advance.
=20
